PackageComment: <text>
CMake target name: QuickLayouts_Attribution_yoga
    Information extracted from:
     /src_dir/qtdeclarative/src/3rdparty/yoga/qt_attribution.json
    Entry index: 0
    Id: yoga
    Name: Yoga
    Description: Facebook's Yoga is an open-source layout engine written in C/C++ that implements a subset of CSS Flexbox. It's designed to be embedded into various frameworks and platforms, providing a fast and efficient way to manage user interface layouts across different environments.
    Qt usage: Used in QtQuick.Layouts
    License: MIT License
    License file: LICENSE
</text>
